{"tid":1245564,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返新工冇咩野做","createTime":"2019-06-20T11:00:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T05:08:42.000Z","uid":155320,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"92458b1b1b93171a909a319d04d496e814b1719d","tid":1245564,"uid":155320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T11:00:23.000Z","msg":"返左差唔多一個禮拜<br />\n4日做既野5個鐘內做得哂<br />\n其餘時間真係係到禁手機上連登 有人行過再扮下野<br />\n但又唔可以禁得咁明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隨時有人會行過<br />\n電腦睇緊咩會比人知 我個位近門口<br />\n日日都冇乜野做自己都唔好意思<br />\n問過老世有冇野做<br />\n佢話慢慢黎啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbackground: FG 15K admin <br />\nno bebefit 打算做到讀完書就quit （part time master)"},{"pid":"8e7f66aed75c2baffb8f2110d536c7df5b9664ee","tid":1245564,"uid":155320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T11:07:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8878cef4f49379442543d7fc25a2f58a12cdb62","tid":1245564,"uid":155320,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T11:08:23.000Z","msg":"好多身邊人都話新工係咁<br />\n1個月冇野做都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c94654de374bc891b2b8d30748a7687367bb6e2","tid":1245564,"uid":43428,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T11:08:54.000Z","msg":"咁你要好好珍惜啦"},{"pid":"3190084f1b225de7885ad778061f334a30593c1b","tid":1245564,"uid":116709,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T11:09:13.000Z","msg":"蜜月期姐, 份份工都係咁"},{"pid":"b1557658995ebc88feb2830ef1c8a88011c67e40","tid":1245564,"uid":155320,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T11:11:17.000Z","msg":"我見左扮工攻略<br />\n進修/股票/睇書/報紙<br />\n<br />\n我書&amp;報紙唔洗諗 太張揚<br />\n進修都好難 電腦都好難用到 手機就一時時 唔想成日禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n股票我冇錢 不過可以研究下既...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我返工冇野做既時候禁手機會唔會唔係咁好<img s